  "detailed_description": "<strong>Man in the Dark</strong> is a single-play TPS game that realistically expresses the dark feeling of the end of the century, set in a place that has turned into a place full of zombies and bizarre creatures. You don't have to go through a lot of learning to experience the great play that sweeps away a swarm of zombies. Kill zombies running from all sides and survive.<br><br><br>- <strong>Unique maps</strong> : 'Abandoned Warehouse, Creepy Town, Rainy Village, Mysterious Fog, Desert of Monster Creatures, and Abandoned Slums' Days and Nights' show a mankind covered with fear and dark. Each map has its own unique atmosphere, and there are many different elements to overcome in order to clear.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/fc6d629a04a7eecb05ca91d1b99a5f73.poster.avif?t=1709879235\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/fc6d629a04a7eecb05ca91d1b99a5f73.webm?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/fc6d629a04a7eecb05ca91d1b99a5f73.mp4?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/9be13b9cb9b6484d959dac2b0ab88da6.poster.avif?t=1709879235\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/9be13b9cb9b6484d959dac2b0ab88da6.webm?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/9be13b9cb9b6484d959dac2b0ab88da6.mp4?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>- <strong>Various weapons</strong> : Each map basically provides 3 kinds guns and grenades. The 3 kinds of guns are configured to match the characteristics of the map and can be used by changing them using a wheelboard.<br><br>- <strong>Equipment</strong> : Certain darkened maps are given Night Vision, Thermal Scope, Flashlight, Hands Flares, etc. to gain visibility.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/80b381eb1a5b225cb1487f84fc1f47ee.poster.avif?t=1709879235\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/80b381eb1a5b225cb1487f84fc1f47ee.webm?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/80b381eb1a5b225cb1487f84fc1f47ee.mp4?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- <strong>Horrifying atmosphere</strong> : Humans who have turned from the darkness of the end to zombies, mysterious creatures and monsters whose is unknown, and infected dogs.. The realistic expression is even more frightening.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/0ee503f1f95f6e52dd2dbd98cc1db712.poster.avif?t=1709879235\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/0ee503f1f95f6e52dd2dbd98cc1db712.webm?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694920/extras/0ee503f1f95f6e52dd2dbd98cc1db712.mp4?t=1709879235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- <strong>Customizing character</strong> : Player can choose a variety of costumes or change the color of each part.",
